# (Removed in audit A-001 — `scripts/pay-order.mjs` used to live here
# as a gitignored helper that hardcoded the test Stellar secret key.
# Replaced by `scripts/e2e-real.mjs`, which reads the secret from
# STELLAR_TEST_SECRET_KEY env. Anyone still carrying a local copy of
# the old file should `rm scripts/pay-order.mjs`.)

# Misc
*.db
merchants.db
server.log

# Quarterly tax / regulatory CSVs (ADR-026 / A4-062). Generated by
# `npm --workspace=@loop/backend run report:quarterly-tax`; the
# operator uploads from `tmp/reports/<quarter>/` to the relevant
# accountant / portal. The artefacts never belong in git — they
# carry per-user totals that the privacy policy treats as PII.
tmp/reports/
